Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.99,0:00:05.78,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Rio...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.21,0:00:08.82,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Încă nu ți-am evaluat abilitățile academice,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.13,0:00:11.32,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,dar mă întrebam dacă poți citi și scrie?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.32,0:00:14.36,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Nu. Nu am studiat niciodată scrisul, deci...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:18.20,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Înțeleg. Atunci, te voi învăța eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.44,0:00:22.85,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Vino la laboratul meu de cercetare după ore. \NEste la subsolul turnului bibliotecii.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.65,0:00:24.92,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Mulțumesc.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.05,0:00:27.65,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Oh, și...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.65,0:00:28.78,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Da?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.78,0:00:32.67,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Mulți copii de aici vin din familii regale sau cu ranguri sociale înalte, deci...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.32,0:00:37.38,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,La început, s-ar putea să fie puțin cam...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.38,0:00:38.29,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Este în regulă.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.29,0:00:39.06,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Ce?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.06,0:00:41.81,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Îmi cunosc locul.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:43.96,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Înțeleg.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.96,0:00:47.54,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Dar dacă ai vreo problemă, nu ezita să vii la mine, te rog, bine?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.54,0:00:48.28,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Desigur.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.68,0:00:52.91,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Bun venit la Academia Regală Beltrum!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:27.13,Dialogue,students,0,0,0,,Ce? Cine este acela?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.13,0:02:28.50,Dialogue,students,0,0,0,,Un elev transferat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.24,0:02:33.50,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Începând de astăzi, un nou elev se va alătura acestei clase. Numele lui este Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.81,0:02:32.28,top,students,0,0,0,,Nu l-am mai văzut până acum.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:36.34,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Copii, să fiți drăguți cu el, bine?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:35.60,top,student A,0,0,0,,Deci este un elev transferat din ghetou, nu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.34,0:02:37.15,Dialogue,student B,0,0,0,,Din ghetou?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.41,0:02:40.97,Dialogue,student B,0,0,0,,Cineva așa josnic ca el va urma cursurile academiei noastre mărețe?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:42.58,Dialogue,student C,0,0,0,,Am auzit că a salvat-o pe prințesa Flora,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.58,0:02:45.50,Dialogue,student C,0,0,0,,deci Maiestatea Sa, regele, a fost de acord cu acest lucru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.76,0:02:51.27,flashback,Philip III,0,0,0,,Ai făcut o treabă excelentă salvându-mi fiica. Îți sunt recunoscător pentru asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:53.07,flashback,Rio,0,0,0,,Aceste cuvinte sunt o adevărată onoare pentru mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.07,0:02:54.84,flashback,Rio,0,0,0,,Îmi aduc o bucurie imensă ca persoană umilă ce sunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.29,0:02:56.15,flashback,Philip III,0,0,0,,Foarte bine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:03:00.35,flashback,Philip III,0,0,0,,În acest caz, îți vom permite să urmezi cursurile școlii primare ale Academiei Regale
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.35,0:03:02.37,flashback,Philip III,0,0,0,,drept elev bursier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.25,0:03:04.10,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:07.61,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Prezintă-te.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:08.31,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Am înțeles.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.76,0:03:09.91,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Numele meu este Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:12.92,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Prin bunătatea care mi-a fost oferită de către Maiestatea Sa, regele,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:15.86,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,mi s-a permis să urmez cursurile acestei școli.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:18.66,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Știu că am foarte multe lipsuri în diferite aspecte,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.57,0:03:21.37,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,dar sper că mă veți privi într-o lumină bună.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.37,0:03:22.13,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Foarte bine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:25.30,Dialogue,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Se pare că măcar poate vorbi la fel ca un servitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:30.55,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Acum, Rio, dacă ai dori să te așezi acolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:31.20,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Desigur.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:42.22,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,În regulă, copii, haide să ne începem lecția.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:44.01,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Să învățăm din greu și astăzi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.01,0:03:45.16,Dialogue,students,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:50.73,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Deschideți-vă caietele și copiați această formulă numerică.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:56.62,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Și acum, încercați să rezolvați aceste probleme singuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.62,0:03:57.91,Dialogue,students,0,0,0,,Am înțeles.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.79,0:04:01.66,Dialogue,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Sunt așa de ușoare.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:06.79,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:09.99,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Nu te suprasolicita foarte tare astăzi, bine?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.99,0:04:12.81,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Desigur. Vă mulțumesc pentru îngrijorare.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:16.77,Dialogue,students,0,0,0,,Nu cred că poate citi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:19.96,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,În regulă, copii. Concentrati-vă la ceea ce lucrați acum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:28.69,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Unde este?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:33.25,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Era un indiciu în acea foaie! Deci unde este acum?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:31.14,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oare acesta e locul?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.19,0:04:33.25,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,{\an8}Dna profesoară Celia?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:34.33,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Vai, Doamne!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:38.26,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Nu știi să citești ce scrie pe acel semn?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:40.88,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Oh, îmi cer scuze.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:42.37,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Nu știu să citesc.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:44.02,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.02,0:04:46.53,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Venisem să vorbim despre lecțiile private, dar...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:51.64,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Da! Ai făcut bine că ai venit. Te așteptam. Așa e!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:54.79,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uitase complet, nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:57.63,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,P-Păi, poți intra.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:04:58.61,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Am înțeles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.89,0:04:59.90,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Te rog să-mi scuzi deranj...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.37,0:05:05.97,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,E-Este doar puțină dezordine momentan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:06.86,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Înțeleg.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:09.99,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,D-De obicei, sunt mult mai organizată.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.48,0:05:14.39,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Just a moment. I'll make us some space.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.39,0:05:17.12,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,There are a lot of \Ndifficult-looking books here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:19.21,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,But you look so young, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:21.31,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Hm? Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.31,0:05:23.53,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,I'm still only twelve, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:24.49,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.49,0:05:27.56,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Really, I should be attending \Nprimary school,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:30.76,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,but I skipped grades and ended up \Ngraduating from high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:32.60,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,You must be quite brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:34.49,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,W-Well, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:40.90,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,I've finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:42.33,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,A-Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:45.82,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,What? This is amazing! \NAll your answers are correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:48.45,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,And you did it so quickly with \Nonly mental calculations...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:51.28,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Well, it was only simple \Nmultiplication and division.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:53.15,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Once I understood how to write \Nthe numbers and symbols...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.15,0:05:54.27,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Simple?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:57.83,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Pretty much the only one in your class \Nwho can do this is Princess Christina.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:06:00.33,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,What? I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.70,0:06:03.13,italics,Rio,0,0,0,,Well, that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:05.76,italics,Rio,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.35,0:06:08.30,italics,Rio,0,0,0,,was a university student, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:09.28,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Rio...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:12.30,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Where did you learn arithmetic?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:15.38,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,From my mother, who died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:16.53,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:19.27,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Your mother was quite cultured.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:20.27,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:23.49,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,She was a kind and warm person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.02,0:06:26.42,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for making you think of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.42,0:06:28.40,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Don't be. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.10,0:06:31.86,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,That's a relief. I'll make \Nus some tea, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:41.08,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Here you are. Please, have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:43.01,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:46.59,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,It's very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:49.64,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,I'm glad you like it! \NWhen you drink a good cup of tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:54.62,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,It just makes you feel happy, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:06:58.55,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:06:59.23,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:02.53,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,How was your first day of academy life?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:05.65,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Please, tell me. Did you have any problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:06.19,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.83,0:07:10.07,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Nothing in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.73,0:07:13.26,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,I see. Well, if there is anything—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.29,0:07:15.75,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,In that case, just one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.75,0:07:16.74,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.53,0:07:20.21,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Will you recommend me some children's books?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:21.92,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Books?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:23.99,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,I want to learn my letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.99,0:07:25.38,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Oh... Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:27.43,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,I'll pick out a few for you from the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.43,0:07:28.11,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:33.47,Dialogue,students,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four, five!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:36.43,Dialogue,Christina,0,0,0,,One! Two! Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:38.56,top,students; background,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four, five!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.67,0:07:38.56,Dialogue,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Four! Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:39.56,Dialogue,instructor,0,0,0,,Stay agile!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:43.33,top,students; background,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four, five!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:43.61,Dialogue,instructor,0,0,0,,Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:44.56,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:49.32,top,students; background,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four, five!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:47.26,Dialogue,instructor,0,0,0,,Come and strike me in any way you see fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.26,0:07:48.07,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:49.32,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.52,0:07:53.64,Dialogue,instructor,0,0,0,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.64,0:07:55.49,Dialogue,students,0,0,0,,What? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:56.28,Dialogue,Roanna,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:57.23,Dialogue,students,0,0,0,,What kind of stance is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.23,0:07:58.16,Dialogue,students,0,0,0,,That stance is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:07:59.75,Dialogue,instructor,0,0,0,,Now, attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:01.62,flashback italics,grandfather,0,0,0,,Now, Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:05.29,flashback,grandfather,0,0,0,,Don't hold back. Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.90,0:08:08.01,flashback,grandfather,0,0,0,,Don't hesitate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:15.88,Dialogue,instructor,0,0,0,,Good swordsmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.63,0:08:18.51,Dialogue,instructor,0,0,0,,Advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.65,0:08:23.66,flashback,grandfather,0,0,0,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:24.94,flashback,grandfather,0,0,0,,Don't dodge it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:27.37,flashback,grandfather,0,0,0,,Drive toward your opponent's chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:38.71,Dialogue,Roana,0,0,0,,Instead of evading to the outside, \Nhe drove toward his opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.71,0:08:40.83,Dialogue,Alphonse,0,0,0,,His form isn't right at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:43.05,Dialogue,Alphonse,0,0,0,,It seems there's no end to his vulgarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:46.33,Dialogue,instructor,0,0,0,,All right. That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.56,0:08:52.16,Dialogue,instructor,0,0,0,,Rio, you have the makings \Nof a knight, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:53.55,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.94,0:08:55.93,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,but I have no interest in joining the knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:56.83,Dialogue,instructor,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:08:59.18,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,I thank you for your kind words.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:00.26,Dialogue,Alphonse,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.26,0:09:01.47,Dialogue,students,0,0,0,,What did he just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:02.22,Dialogue,students,0,0,0,,That's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.70,0:09:06.60,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:07.23,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:09.24,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,You're even studious after classes end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.83,0:09:11.94,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,End-of-term exams are coming up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:16.58,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,You've only just enrolled here. You don't \Nneed to worry about your grades too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.58,0:09:17.49,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:19.99,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,But I'll give it everything I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.86,0:09:22.34,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:26.77,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Does everyone have an examination paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:28.18,Dialogue,students,0,0,0,,Yes, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.18,0:09:29.38,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Then, begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:31.00,Dialogue,students,0,0,0,,Yikes! Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.82,0:09:32.69,top,students,0,0,0,,One, two, three...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.69,0:09:35.11,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Mouths closed, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:43.13,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Everyone, do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.52,0:09:57.15,italics,Haruto,0,0,0,,Mii...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.51,0:09:58.36,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,...chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:00.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:01.66,Dialogue,students,0,0,0,,Is that him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:02.42,Dialogue,students,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.42,0:10:04.44,Dialogue,students,0,0,0,,A kid from the slums enrolled here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.44,0:10:06.65,Dialogue,students,0,0,0,,His Majesty, the King, is pretty eccentric.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:10.70,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Ayase Miharu was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.53,0:10:14.24,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Amakawa Haruto's childhood friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.16,0:10:19.92,italics,Rio,0,0,0,,But when Haruto's parents divorced, \Nthe two of them were separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:24.33,italics,Haruto,0,0,0,,Then I saw Mii-chan again in high school...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.80,0:10:25.87,italics,Haruto,0,0,0,,and that was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:29.25,italics,Haruto,0,0,0,,She never came back to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:32.65,italics,Haruto,0,0,0,,It was as though she'd erased \Nherself from my sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.47,0:10:36.65,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,And what of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.10,0:10:39.15,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Amakawa Haruto is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.58,0:10:40.92,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Right now, I am Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:43.09,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,I'm not Amakawa Haruto anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:44.97,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:46.94,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,I will live through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:48.97,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,I will be tenacious and strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:50.89,Dialogue,students,0,0,0,,This can't be right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.89,0:10:51.80,Dialogue,students,0,0,0,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:52.63,Dialogue,students,0,0,0,,That guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:53.88,Dialogue,students,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:55.38,Dialogue,students,0,0,0,,Alongside Princess Christina?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:56.40,Dialogue,students,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:57.85,Dialogue,Roana,0,0,0,,I'm third?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:11:01.13,Dialogue,Alphonse,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding me! \NThis must be some kind of mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.13,0:11:02.59,Dialogue,student A,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:04.18,Dialogue,student A,0,0,0,,Hey, he's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:06.57,Dialogue,Alphonse,0,0,0,,You! What impropriety have you perpetrated?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.57,0:11:08.39,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:09.39,Dialogue,Alphonse,0,0,0,,That!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:10.85,Dialogue,Alphonse,0,0,0,,A commoner like you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:14.22,Dialogue,Alphonse,0,0,0,,could never stand with Princess Christina \Nat the top of the class!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:15.65,Dialogue,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Anything other than fraud is unthinkable!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:16.53,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Top of the class?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:19.40,Dialogue,Alphonse,0,0,0,,You must have used some kind of dirty trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.69,0:11:22.20,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,I simply took the exam, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:23.10,Dialogue,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:24.52,Dialogue,Roanna,0,0,0,,Leave it, Alphonse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:28.87,Dialogue,Roanna,0,0,0,,The jealousy of a gentleman is unsightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.72,0:11:32.45,Dialogue,Alphonse,0,0,0,,I-I can't let this pass unchallenged! \NI will have this injustice—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.45,0:11:34.69,Dialogue,Christina,0,0,0,,Do you have any concrete evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:36.50,Dialogue,Alphonse,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:40.35,Dialogue,Christina,0,0,0,,Unsubstantiated allegations only serve to\N sully the dignity of the academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:42.09,top,Alphonse,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.32,0:11:45.22,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,This achievement is the result \Nof Rio's hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:47.41,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,I can attest to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:49.35,Dialogue,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Professor Celia...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:51.26,Dialogue,Alphonse,0,0,0,,I will never accept this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:53.79,Dialogue,student A,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:54.86,Dialogue,students,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.33,0:11:57.20,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Thank you for—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:12:00.27,Dialogue,Roanna,0,0,0,,It was nothing. And I didn't \Nintervene for your sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.27,0:12:01.30,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.94,0:12:03.60,Dialogue,Roanna,0,0,0,,You won't beat me next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.65,0:12:07.55,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:09.82,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Congratulations on placing \Nfirst in the end-of-term exams!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.82,0:12:11.13,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:12.76,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:15.23,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,I'm a little worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:16.09,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:16.63,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:21.63,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,When I think that even more students may \Nlook for ways to find fault with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.33,0:12:23.88,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,I'm used to it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.88,0:12:24.63,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:27.85,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,This bullying by nobles shows poor \Ncharacter on their part, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.15,0:12:33.14,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Professor Celia, you said that you excelled. \NDid anything similar happen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:38.73,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Well, this and that from those of a higher \Nsocial standing and their followers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:40.23,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,I ignored all of it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:41.42,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:44.27,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,I-In my case, I had friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.27,0:12:46.42,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Then, I'll be fine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.42,0:12:47.45,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:49.61,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,I have you, Professor Celia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.09,0:12:50.68,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.42,0:12:52.04,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.94,0:12:54.58,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Oh, Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:55.08,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:58.72,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,You're making fun of me, aren't you?\N Treating me like a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:13:01.35,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,But you're older than me, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.35,0:13:09.19,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, but... well... it means you \Nthink of me as a friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.19,0:13:09.95,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:12.26,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Would you rather I didn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.26,0:13:14.15,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,I... don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.15,0:13:14.56,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:17.56,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,I... don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:20.55,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Will you say it just one more time, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:21.57,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:25.82,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,I said I don't mind! You're so mean, Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:28.12,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Figure it out from the mood,\N can't you? Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:29.09,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:35.08,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,If ever I'm in trouble, advise me as \Nmy teacher and as my friend, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:37.58,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,O-Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:42.95,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,When you're about to cry from all \Nthe bullying, I'll take you to my bosom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,0:13:47.47,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,You're small, so in terms of positioning, \Nyou do seem perfect for clinging to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:51.86,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Don't say "small"! I'm still growing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.59,0:13:53.74,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Oh, we're the perfect heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:56.03,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:14:00.46,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Oh, Rio, you silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.16,0:14:06.95,top,instructor,0,0,0,,An exhibition tournament between the knights\N of the realm will be held again this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:11.56,Dialogue,instructor,0,0,0,,Representatives for the primary school \Ndivision have been selected from this class.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.56,0:14:13.95,Dialogue,instructor,0,0,0,,If your name is called, step forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:16.83,Dialogue,instructor,0,0,0,,Sixth-year, Alphonse Rodan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:17.89,Dialogue,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.89,0:14:20.30,Dialogue,instructor,0,0,0,,Fifth-year, Stewart Huguenot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:20.92,Dialogue,Stewart,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.73,0:14:23.64,Dialogue,instructor,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:24.85,Dialogue,instructor,0,0,0,,Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:27.84,Dialogue,students,0,0,0,,What? It can't be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:26.78,Dialogue,instructor,0,0,0,,Step forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:27.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:28.84,Dialogue,students,0,0,0,,Him? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:30.99,Dialogue,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.99,0:14:32.08,Dialogue,instructor,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:33.56,Dialogue,Alphonse,0,0,0,,I cannot accept this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.79,0:14:38.13,Dialogue,Alphonse,0,0,0,,For someone so lowly to have been chosen to \Nparticipate in a knightly tournament...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.99,0:14:37.45,top,students; background,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.13,0:14:39.84,Dialogue,Alphonse,0,0,0,,It is a disgrace!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:43.03,Dialogue,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Besides, he can't even use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:45.73,Dialogue,instructor,0,0,0,,It has already been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.97,0:14:47.45,Dialogue,instructor,0,0,0,,No objections will be entertained.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:48.40,Dialogue,students; background,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:52.16,Dialogue,students; background,0,0,0,,I just can't accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:55.58,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,I heard you'll be participating \Nin the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:58.47,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Yes, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.45,0:15:01.30,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,If you do well in the tournament,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:05.56,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,the knights may scout you even \Nbefore you graduate, you... know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.24,0:15:09.52,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,I have no intention of becoming a knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.52,0:15:10.51,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Rio...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:11.30,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:14.16,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,You've gotten taller, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:14.78,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:18.15,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose it has \Nbeen five years already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.65,0:15:20.86,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Professor...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.86,0:15:21.85,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.11,0:15:24.10,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,You're still just as small \Nas ever, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:27.20,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Don't say "small"! \NI'm still growing, I tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.20,0:15:28.97,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,You said the same thing five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:30.38,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.38,0:15:31.86,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,The tea will get cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:32.86,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:36.72,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Such a lovely aroma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:39.96,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,It's so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:41.29,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,They're the same leaves,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:44.79,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,but when you make the tea, Rio, \Nthe scent is completely different!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:47.42,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,I simply follow the instructions\N I read in a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:51.33,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,You say you have no intention \Nof becoming a knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.33,0:15:53.05,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,What will you do after you graduate?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:54.65,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,I thought I'd go on a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.65,0:15:55.62,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.62,0:15:57.40,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,There's somewhere I'd like to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.83,0:16:00.62,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Then... you plan to leave this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.62,0:16:01.87,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,This country...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.99,0:16:04.69,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,is difficult for me to live in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.32,0:16:07.28,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,That may be so, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:11.53,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Why don't you work here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:12.11,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:14.80,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Without you around, \Nall sorts of things will go wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:16.12,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:19.31,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,You see? The way you tidied here...\N It's so clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:21.33,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,And you make such wonderful tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:25.63,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,You always chide me when I get too \Ncaught up in my research. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:27.59,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,I'm grateful for your consideration, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.59,0:16:31.25,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Professor, sooner or later you'll \Nenter into marriage talks, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:32.86,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,What's this all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.86,0:16:36.88,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be good to have some \Nunknown commoner in your research lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:40.89,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,I've no intention of getting \Nmarried for a long time, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.11,0:16:44.02,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure you're free \Nto do as you like, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:47.26,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Hey! You're thinking I'm going to miss \Nmy chance to get married, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.87,0:16:51.94,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Professor Celia, you look so youthful \Nand lovely, I'm sure you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.29,0:16:55.84,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,So you're saying I look like a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.59,0:16:59.58,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Not at all. You're a charming woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:02.33,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,D-Don't tease me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:03.06,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:07.58,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Oh! Um, well... Where is it \Nthat you want to go, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:10.54,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,My parents' homeland, the Yagumo region.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:15.09,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Yagumo? The place at the \Nedge of the wilderness?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.03,0:17:17.67,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:24.68,flashback,Ayame,0,0,0,,When you're bigger, I'll take you there.\N It's a place called Yagumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:27.19,flashback,Rio; 5 yo,0,0,0,,Really? You promised, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:28.97,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:32.53,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,I-It's only a plan at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:34.74,italics,Celia,0,0,0,,Rio...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:40.85,Dialogue,Emerle,0,0,0,,Now, the tournament between the \Nglorious knights of the realm
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.85,0:17:43.79,Dialogue,Emerle,0,0,0,,and the students of the \NRoyal Academy will begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.43,0:17:51.17,Dialogue,Emerle,0,0,0,,And I, Alfred Emerle, unworthy as \NI am, will serve as referee today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:53.42,Dialogue,nobles,0,0,0,,As noble as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.05,0:17:55.42,Dialogue,girls,0,0,0,,Emerle-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.06,0:18:00.43,Dialogue,Emerle,0,0,0,,Beltrum Royal Academy primary school! \NFirst challenger, Rio! Stand forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:07.81,Dialogue,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't put on a pathetic \Nperformance out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:10.26,Dialogue,Alphonse,0,0,0,,You'll lower people's opinions of me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.72,0:18:13.32,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,I will do my best not to \Nfight an unsightly match.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:16.44,Dialogue,Alphonse,0,0,0,,No one is expecting anything from you anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.63,0:18:20.74,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:22.49,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Keep it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.09,0:18:24.85,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,I am ready to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:25.75,Dialogue,Emerle,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:27.50,Dialogue,Emerle,0,0,0,,And from the Knights of the Royal Guard,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:28.50,Dialogue,Emerle,0,0,0,,the first challenger,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:29.72,Dialogue,Emerle,0,0,0,,Charles Arbor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.91,0:18:37.81,Dialogue,Charles,0,0,0,,I knew you'd enrolled in the academy,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:40.38,Dialogue,Charles,0,0,0,,but I'd never have imagined that the \Ndirty little brat from back then
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.38,0:18:42.80,Dialogue,Charles,0,0,0,,would be my opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:45.43,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,I owe you a debt for your care of me back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.66,0:18:50.00,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,I was so very sorry I couldn't \Nhave been of more help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:52.61,Dialogue,Emerle,0,0,0,,Cease your chatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:55.10,Dialogue,Emerle,0,0,0,,Challengers at the ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.50,0:18:59.83,italics,Emerle,0,0,0,,What is that stance?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.73,0:19:03.00,italics,Charles,0,0,0,,He doesn't have a shield. Is he mocking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.87,0:19:04.91,Dialogue,Emerle,0,0,0,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:11.08,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Rio's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.61,0:19:13.59,Dialogue,Roanna,0,0,0,,He's staying calm and parrying the blows.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:18.88,italics,Charles,0,0,0,,Because of you, I was punished \Nwith a demotion five years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.33,0:19:21.47,italics,Charles,0,0,0,,I will never forget that humiliation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:23.22,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,H-Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:26.14,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,How could a knight fight so \Nseriously against a student?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:29.34,Dialogue,instructor,0,0,0,,Now, Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.34,0:19:29.93,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:32.02,Dialogue,Charles,0,0,0,,This will finish you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.23,0:19:40.20,Dialogue,Emerle,0,0,0,,Hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.48,0:19:43.27,Dialogue,Emerle,0,0,0,,The winner, representing the academy, is Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.83,0:19:44.99,Dialogue,Charles,0,0,0,,W-Wait, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:47.18,Dialogue,Charles,0,0,0,,I let down my guard. That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:48.05,Dialogue,Emerle,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.84,0:19:49.82,Dialogue,Charles,0,0,0,,I'll fight for real next—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:51.08,Dialogue,Emerle,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:52.58,Dialogue,Emerle,0,0,0,,A loss is a loss!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:54.73,Dialogue,Charles,0,0,0,,Alfred...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:19:55.94,Dialogue,Emerle,0,0,0,,Charles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.94,0:19:58.30,Dialogue,Emerle,0,0,0,,If you are a member of the honorable \NKnights of the Royal Guard,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:01.31,Dialogue,Emerle,0,0,0,,you will graciously accept your \Ndefeat and take your leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.77,0:20:06.47,Dialogue,Charles,0,0,0,,I-I admit my defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.98,0:20:08.55,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Thank you for the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:10.23,Dialogue,Emerle,0,0,0,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:12.03,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Amazing! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:14.11,Dialogue,instructor,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:22.24,italics,Emerle,0,0,0,,Rio, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:24.49,italics,Emerle,0,0,0,,I look forward to his future.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.18,0:20:30.79,Dialogue,Charles,0,0,0,,Blast that annoying brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:34.37,Dialogue,Charles,0,0,0,,If I'd been serious, I would have won!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:39.30,Dialogue,Reiss,0,0,0,,In that sort of situation, it isn't so \Nbad to let the students take the glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:42.13,Dialogue,Reiss,0,0,0,,With no understanding\N of such consideration,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.37,0:20:45.21,Dialogue,Reiss,0,0,0,,in the end, the other Knights \Nof the Royal Guard all won.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.21,0:20:47.14,Dialogue,Reiss,0,0,0,,Dear, dear. How childish of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:48.41,Dialogue,Charles,0,0,0,,Th-That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.41,0:20:50.52,Dialogue,Charles,0,0,0,,I let him take the glory!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:52.82,Dialogue,Charles,0,0,0,,Just as you'd expect from the Honorable \NAmbassador of the Proxia Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.82,0:20:54.17,Dialogue,Charles,0,0,0,,You understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:59.45,Dialogue,Reiss,0,0,0,,And that student who fought against you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:00.16,Dialogue,Charles,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:02.57,Dialogue,Reiss,0,0,0,,He certainly moved very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:05.72,Dialogue,Charles,0,0,0,,That brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:06.61,Dialogue,Charles,0,0,0,,Five years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.61,0:21:10.37,Dialogue,Charles,0,0,0,,it was thought he might have been \Ninvolved in Princess Flora's kidnapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:14.87,Dialogue,Charles,0,0,0,,At the time, I investigated vigorously, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.87,0:21:17.17,Dialogue,Charles,0,0,0,,In the end, he never talked.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:17.88,Dialogue,Reiss,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:20.71,Dialogue,Reiss,0,0,0,,So you two were fated \Nto face each other, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:22.36,Dialogue,Charles,0,0,0,,I don't know about fated.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.43,0:21:28.35,italics,Reiss,0,0,0,,I see. From back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.30,0:21:36.23,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,I hope he comes soon. I need \Nto celebrate his win with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.83,0:21:37.48,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.35,0:21:43.11,Dialogue,Celia,0,0,0,,I wonder where he's going.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.99,0:21:48.30,Dialogue,younger female student,0,0,0,,H-Here. Please, read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:49.46,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.46,0:21:53.48,Dialogue,younger female student,0,0,0,,Y-Yesterday's match! \NYou were so... so very dashing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.26,0:21:56.66,Dialogue,younger female student,0,0,0,,So gallant!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.66,0:21:57.90,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Oh, hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.64,0:21:59.98,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,Stai, așteaptă!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.42,0:23:37.97,Dialogue,Rio,0,0,0,,"Regatul minciunilor."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.49,0:00:04.48,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,Anul 991 al Erei Sfinte
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.05,0:01:14.22,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,Cronicile spiritului
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:29.00,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,Academia Regală
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:06.95,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,Anul 996 al Erei Sfinte
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:39.98,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,Data viitoare
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:39.98,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,Regatul minciunilor
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.98,0:23:42.08,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,Cronicile spiritului
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.98,0:23:42.08,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,O bandă desenată bonus, încântătoare
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.98,0:23:50.25,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,Realizată de: Minazuki Futago
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.08,0:23:42.48,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,holbare
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.60,0:23:44.50,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,Se uită la mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.50,0:23:48.00,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,N-Nu mă uit la tine că te plac sau ceva. Să nu înțelegi greșit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.25,0:23:48.00,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,Să nu înțelegi greșit, ai auzit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.00,0:23:50.25,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,Ce? Bine...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.59,0:23:50.25,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,Nu o voi face...
